        = The One Where We're Trapped On TV\n |RTitle          = <ref>{{Cite tweet |number=1214634320616448002 |user=NICKZANO |title=Gang gang, this ep is \ud83d\udcaf [caption from photo showing script page for episode] |author-link=Nick Zano |date=January 7, 2020 |access-date=January 19, 2020 |last=Zano |first=Nick}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy      = [[Marc Guggenheim]]\n |WrittenBy       = Grainne Godfree & James Eagan\n |OriginalAirDate = \n |ProdCode        = T13.21914\n |Viewers         =\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = CF905C\n}}\n{{Episode list/sublist|Legends of Tomorrow (season 5)\n |EpisodeNumber   = 82\n |EpisodeNumber2  = 14\n |Title           = Swan Thong\n |RTitle          = <ref name=\"FinaleScript\">{{Cite tweet |number=1218257734161715201 |user=ketomizu |title=Aaaand finally, #LegendsOfTomorrow episode 515 is now in production! Our finale is written by myself and @morganfaust and directed by @kevmock |author-link=Keto Shimizu |date=January 17, 2020 |last=Shimizu |first=Keto}}</ref>\n |DirectedBy      = Kevin Mock\n |WrittenBy       = Keto Shimizu & Morgan Faust\n |OriginalAirDate = \n |ProdCode        = T13.21915\n |Viewers         =\n |ShortSummary    = \n |LineColor       = CF905C\n}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Cast and characters ==\n{{Main|List of Legends of Tomorrow characters}}\n{{Columns-start|num=2}}\n\n=== Main ===\n* [[Brandon Routh]] as [[Ray Palmer (Arrowverse)|Ray Palmer / Atom]]{{efn|Routh is credited through \"[[Romeo v Juliet: Dawn of Justness]]\". Routh also portrayed the Earth-96 [[Superman Returns|Clark Kent / Superman]] in \"[[Crisis on Infinite Earths (Arrowverse)|Crisis on Infinite Earths: Part Five]]\".}}<ref name=\"Day 1\" />\n* [[Caity Lotz]] as [[Sara Lance|<!-- don't delink -->Sara Lance / White Canary]]<ref name=\"Lotz\" />\n* [[Maisie Richardson-Sellers]] as [[Charlie (Arrowverse)|Charlie]] / [[Clotho]]<ref name=\"Sellers\" />\n* [[Tala Ashe]] as [[Zari Tomaz|Zari Tarazi]]<ref name=\"new Zari\" />\n* [[Jes Macallan]] as [[Ava Sharpe]]<ref name=\"Macallan\" />\n* [[Courtney Ford]] as [[Nora Darhk]]<ref name=\"Ford\" />{{efn|Ford is credited through \"[[Romeo v Juliet: Dawn of Justness]]\". Ford also portrayed [[Marie Antoinette]] in \"A Head of Her Time\".}}\n* Olivia Swann as [[Astra Logue (Arrowverse)|Astra Logue]]<ref name=\"SwannEW\" />\n* [[Amy Pemberton|Amy Louise Pemberton]] as [[Gideon (Legends of Tomorrow)|Gideon]]<ref name=\"Pemberton\" />\n* [[Nick Zano]] as [[Nate Heywood (Arrowverse)|Nate Heywood / Steel]]<ref name=\"Day 1\" />\n* [[Dominic Purcell]] as [[Mick Rory (Arrowverse)|Mick Rory / Heat Wave]]<ref name=\"Day 1\" />\n* [[Matt Ryan (actor)|Matt Ryan]] as [[John Constantine (Arrowverse)|John Constantine]]<ref name=\"Ryan\" />\n{{Column}}\n\n=== Recurring ===\n* Shayan Sobhian as [[Behrad Tarazi]]<ref name=\"EW\" />\n* Adam Tsekhman as [[Gary Green (Arrowverse)|Gary Green]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B0H72enAoxk/ |title=We\u2019re baaaack! While you guys enjoy comic con, we fight the baddies. The brilliant @kevmock with the cameo. @cw_legendsoftomorrow #garygreen |last=Tsekhman |first=Adam |date=July 21, 2019 |website=[[Instagram]] |access-date=July 21, 2019}}</ref>\n* [[Joanna Vanderham]] as [[Atropos]]<ref name=\"Deadline\">[https://deadline.com/2020/01/dcs-legends-of-tomorrow-joanna-vanderham-season-5-villain-1202832668/ \"\u2018DC\u2019s Legends Of Tomorrow\u2019 Adds Joanna Vanderham As Season 5 Villain\" - Deadline]</ref>\n{{Columns-end}}\n\n=== Guest ===\n{{columns-list|colwidth=30em|\n* [[Grant Gustin]] as [[Barry Allen (Arrowverse)|Barry Allen / Flash]]<ref name=\"LegendsEpPics\" />\n* [[Melissa Benoist]] as [[Supergirl (Arrowverse)|Kara Zor-El / Kara Danvers / Supergirl]]<ref name=\"LegendsEpPics\" />\n* [[Ruby Rose]] as [[Kate Kane (Arrowverse)|Kate Kane / Batwoman]]\n* [[LaMonica Garrett]] as [[Anti-Monitor (Arrowverse)|Mobius / Anti-Monitor]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cbr.com/crisis-infinite-earths-lamonica-garrett-anti-moni