/the-cw-sets-fall-premiere-dates-batwoman-supergirl-the-flash-nancy-drew-1202633821/ |title=The CW Sets Fall Premiere Dates: 'Batwoman', 'Supergirl', 'The Flash', 'Nancy Drew', More |last=Petski |first=Denise |date=June 17, 2019 |website=Deadline Hollywood |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190618053243/https://deadline.com/2019/06/the-cw-sets-fall-premiere-dates-batwoman-supergirl-the-flash-nancy-drew-1202633821/ |archive-date=June 18, 2019 |access-date=June 17, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Littlefield\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/08/batwoman-casting-sam-littlefield-joins-gotham-city-underworld-1202701005/ |title='Batwoman' Casting: Sam Littlefield Joins Gotham City Underworld |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |date=August 21, 2019 |website=Deadline Hollywood |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190821210331/https://deadline.com/2019/08/batwoman-casting-sam-littlefield-joins-gotham-city-underworld-1202701005/ |archive-date=August 21, 2019 |access-date=August 21, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RachelMaddow\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/batwoman-rachel-maddow-will-be-the-gossip-in-gotham-citys-ear-1202752707/ |title=\u2018Batwoman\u2019: Rachel Maddow Will Be The Gossip In Gotham City\u2019s Ear |last=Boucher |first=Geoff |date=October 4, 2019 |website=Deadline Hollywood |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191005014101/https://deadline.com/2019/10/batwoman-rachel-maddow-will-be-the-gossip-in-gotham-citys-ear-1202752707/ |archive-date=October 5, 2019 |access-date=October 4, 2019}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SebastianRoch\u00e9\">{{Cite web |url=https://deadline.com/2019/10/sebastian-roche-batwoman-cast-cw-1202752849/ |title=Sebastian Roch\u00e9 Back In CW Fold, Joins 'Batwoman' Cast In Recurring Role |last=Hipes |first=Patrick |date=October 4, 2019 |website=Deadline Hollywood |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191005131327/https://deadline.com/2019/10/sebast