inin 1990-1991|1990-91]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Bronze medal icon.svg|20px|Third place]]\n|align=center| \n|align=center|[[1990\u201391 Women's IHF Cup|IHF]]||1/4-finals\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1991-1992|1991-92]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| 6th\n|align=center| \n|align=center|[[1991\u201392 Women's IHF Cup|IHF]]||1/2-finals\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1992-1993|1992-93]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| 6th\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|20px]] ''Finalist''\n|align=center colspan=\"2\"|''Not qualified''\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1993-1994|1993-94]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal icon.svg|20px|Runner-up]]\n|align=center| 4th\n|align=center|[[1993\u201394 EHF Women's Cup Winners' Cup|CC]]||1/2-finals\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1994-1995|1994-95]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Bronze medal icon.svg|20px|Third place]]\n|align=center| 4th\n|align=center|[[1994\u201395 Women's EHF Cup|EHF]]||1/4-finals\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1995-1996|1995-96]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal icon.svg|20px|Runner-up]]\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|20px]] ''Finalist''\n|align=center|[[1995/96 Women's EHF City Cup|CC]]||[[File:Gold medal with cup.svg|20px]] '''Winner'''\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1996-1997|1996-97]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal icon.svg|20px|Runner-up]]\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|20px]] ''Finalist''\n|align=center|[[1996/97 Women's EHF City Cup|CC]]||1/2-finals\n|-\n| [[Liga Na\u021bional\u0103 de handbal feminin 1997-1998|1997-98]]\n| bgcolor=#ddffdd| LN\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal icon.svg|20px|Runner-up]]\n|align=center| [[File:Silver medal with cup.svg|20px]] ''Finalist''\n|align=center|[[1997\u201398 EHF